title: Who needs Mp3?
comment: This is awesome!!! I can now listen to all my favourite remixes that are only on youtube. I also use it for Motzart when im relaxing or doing homework.  I use it for Dubstep and rock when im playing a game. I make playlists of songs from games and mainly just music I like.  It is easy to use and it doesn't keep asking you for your YT accout , like most of these "background YT" apps. I wish you could order the songs , and switch to them and continue listing to the whole playlist.

title: Volume resets to 50% after each song
comment: As Nexus 5 user with little storage, I have to use online services. This is the best of its kind (pvstar+, tubeplayer, etc.). However there is an in-app (not android) volume,  which defaults to 50% on each new song. Extremely annoying especially since this default value cannot be changed. I have written to the developer but he doesn't want to change it, so 4 stars till its fixed.

title: Brilliant
comment: Was looking for an app that would stream just the audio from YouTube, as video would not be possible on my slow mobile data network. This app does exactly that, and the streaming is very smooth with hardly any buffering happening. Lots of scope for improvement though in terms of language (grammar) and features (unable to navigate to a particular time point in an audio) . I can help the developer with the English part if needed. All the best!  ***Edit:  The way you've dedicated the app to your wife is very sweet. You are lucky, she is indeed lovely in the photo :-)
